<script type="application/ld+json">[{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"Organization","name":"APKPure","url":"https://apkpure.net","logo":"https://static.cdnpure.com/www/static/imgs/logo_new.png","sameAs":["https://www.facebook.com/APKPureOfficial","https://twitter.com/apkpure","https://vk.com/apkpurevk","https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbCOKdnt1yYk4S3I4a034XQ"]},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"WebSite","name":"APKPure","url":"https://apkpure.net","potentialAction":{"@type":"SearchAction","target":"https://apkpure.net/search?q={search_term_string}","query-input":"required name=search_term_string"}},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://apkpure.net/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"Apps","item":"https://apkpure.net/app"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"name":"Entertainment","item":"https://apkpure.net/entertainment"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":4,"name":"RPG Maker Plugin for JoiPlay"}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"MobileApplication","name":"RPG Maker Plugin for JoiPlay","description":"Developed by JoiPlay, this add-on focuses on dependable compatibility for RPG Maker XP, VX, and VX Ace projects on Android. It works with a front-end app and does not function on its own. Games are not included, so you need legally obtained game files to play. If you are searching for the RPG Maker Plugin for JoiPlay APK, the key points below show what it offers.  Adds support for RPG Maker XP, VX, and VX Ace projects on Android front-ends.  Integrates with JoiPlay or compatible front-end apps; not a standalone application.  Based on android-mkxp and mkxp forks under GNU GPL v2.0 license.  Requires legally obtained game files; games are not included within the plugin.  Works alongside a front-end to run projects without PC access.  Clear Terms of Service and Privacy Policy available from the developer.RPG Maker XP/VX/VX Ace supportThis plugin enables projects built with RPG Maker XP, VX, and VX Ace to run through compatible front-end apps on Android. With RPG Maker Plugin for JoiPlay, you point your front-end to a game’s folder and the plugin handles engine behavior for consistent play. It suits users who want to revisit classic projects on mobile with the files they already own.Front-end integrationThe plugin is designed to work with JoiPlay or another compatible front-end, so it does not operate on its own. It is based on forks of android-mkxp and mkxp under the GNU GPL v2.0, providing transparency about its foundations. The RPG Maker Plugin for JoiPlay latest version helps keep support current across XP, VX, and VX Ace projects.Download and install RPG Maker Plugin for JoiPlayAPKPure provides the package, so you can download RPG Maker Plugin for JoiPlay with a few taps. The download time depends on your connection, and installation typically completes quickly. During installation, Android may ask for permission to install apps from this source. After it finishes, use your chosen front-end to load your legally obtained RPG Maker project files.Install the plugin first, then open a front-end app like JoiPlay to start testing your projects. If a game doesn’t launch, confirm it targets XP, VX, or VX Ace and that the files are intact. Keep storage organized so your front-end can find game folders without issues.","version":"1.20.53-patreon","operatingSystem":"ANDROID","applicationCategory":"EntertainmentApplication","applicationSubCategory":"Entertainment","offers":{"@type":"Offer","price":"0.00","priceCurrency":"USD"},"datePublished":"2024-12-08","aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"10.0","ratingCount":1,"bestRating":10,"worstRating":1},"publisher":{"@type":"Thing","name":"JoiPlay"},"interactionStatistic":{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"http://schema.org/DownloadAction","userInteractionCount":97000},"inLanguage":[{"@type":"Language","name":"es"},{"@type":"Language","